<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>469</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Tu lio nungak leng le val, Kam ram ca zeidah na tuah cio, A mui mi
 ram, Zoh ah nan ngaih a chia lo maw? mit-thli he, Nitin thlacam kan herh.

[C1]
   A dawh ve ko tung kan Lairam mui te zong hi, Zei hen a tu tiang
   Jesuh mui a len lo, Ho hen kan rinh kan ram ca-ah Jesuh nih, Nangmah
   theng an herh.

[V2]
 Nang na tel lo a si le, A mui chin lai kanmah ruang ah, Maw u le nau,
 Tih a nung tuk tu lio kan nunnak caan hi, Biatak thlarau kan herh.

[C2]
   A dawh ve ko tung kan Lairam mui te zong hi, Zei hen a tu tiang
   Jesuh mui a len lo, Ho hen kan rinh kan ram ca-ah Jesuh nih, Nangmah
   theng an herh.

[V3]
 Ram thar ceuter tu dingah, Nang le kei nih tuanvo kan ngei, Na hngal
 cang maw? Ceu ve cang seh kan Lairam hi Jesuh nih, Rian tha bik a kan
 fial.

[C3]
   A dawh ve ko tung kan Lairam mui te zong hi, Zei hen a tu tiang
   Jesuh mui a len lo, Ho hen kan rinh kan ram ca-ah Jesuh nih, Nangmah
   theng an herh.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>NANGMAH THENG AN HERH CH469</title>
</song>